<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mission – MindConnect</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --green: #10a37f;
            --green-dark: #0c8a6b;
            --green-light: #e8f7f3;
            --ink: #0f1923;
            --ink2: #374151;
            --muted: #6b7280;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --surface: #f9fafb;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--white); color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
 
        header { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); z-index: 999; }
        nav { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; height: 68px; }
        .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); text-decoration: none; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }
        .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink2); font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px; padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .nav-links a:hover { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
        .nav-links a.active { color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; background: var(--green-light); }
        .nav-cta { background: var(--green) !important; color: white !important; padding: 9px 18px !important; border-radius: 8px !important; }
        .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--green-dark) !important; color: white !important; }
 
        /* MISSION HERO - Full bleed green */
        .mission-hero {
            padding-top: 68px;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0c8a6b 0%, #10a37f 50%, #0f9672 100%);
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .mission-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        }
        .mission-hero-inner {
            max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 24px 80px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
        }
        .breadcrumb { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); text-decoration: none; }
        .mission-hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 58px); font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.025em; margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .mission-hero p { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height: 1.65; }
 
        .mission-hero-right {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px;
        }
        .pullquote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 22px; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5;
            color: white; margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .pullquote-attr { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 500; }
 
        /* THE PROBLEM */
        .problem-section { padding: 100px 0; }
        .problem-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
        .section-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background: var(--green); color: white; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .section-sub { font-size: 17px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }
 
        .problem-grid {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; margin-top: 60px; align-items: start;
        }
        .problem-text p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .problem-text p strong { color: var(--ink); }
 
        .stat-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
        .big-stat-card {
            background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 32px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }
        .big-stat-num {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--green); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 120px;
        }
        .big-stat-text h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .big-stat-text p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }
 
        /* SOLUTION */
        .solution-section { background: var(--surface); padding: 100px 0; }
        .solution-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
 
        .pillars-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 56px; }
        .pillar-card {
            background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }
        .pillar-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
        .pillar-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .pillar-card h3 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .pillar-card p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
 
        /* VISION */
        .vision-section { padding: 100px 0; }
        .vision-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; text-align: center; }
        .vision-inner h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 52px);
            font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.025em; margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .vision-inner p { font-size: 18px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 16px; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
 
        .values-grid {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 56px; text-align: left;
        }
        .value-card {
            background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px;
            display: flex; gap: 16px;
        }
        .value-card-icon { font-size: 28px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .value-card h4 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .value-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
 
        .btn-primary { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; background: var(--green); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; margin-top: 48px; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--green-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(16,163,127,0.3); }
 
        footer { background: #090e14; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); padding: 36px 0; }
        .footer-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
        .footer-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: white; }
        .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
        .footer-links a { text-decoration: none; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 14px; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .footer-links a:hover { color: white; }
 
        .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: all 0.7s ease; }
        .reveal.in-view { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
 
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .mission-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
            .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
 
<header>
    <nav>
        <a href="index.html" class="logo">MindConnect</a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="services.html">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="network.html">Network</a></li>
            <li><a href="mission.html" class="active">Mission</a></li>
            <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="contact.html" class="nav-cta">Get Started</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>
 
<!-- HERO -->
<div class="mission-hero">
    <div class="mission-hero-inner">
        <div>
            <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a> / Mission</div>
            <h1>Transforming Mental Health Care</h1>
            <p>We exist because too many people face mental health challenges without the support they need. MindConnect is changing that — one person at a time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-hero-right">
            <div class="pullquote">"No one should have to navigate the complexity of mental healthcare alone — especially those who already face the most barriers."</div>
            <div class="pullquote-attr">— MindConnect Founding Principle</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
 
<!-- THE PROBLEM -->
<section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-inner">
        <div class="section-tag reveal">The Challenge</div>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Mental Illness is a National Crisis</h2>
        <div class="problem-grid">
            <div class="problem-text reveal">
                <p>The United States faces a <strong>mental health epidemic</strong> that disproportionately impacts medically underserved and rural communities. Too many people are slipping through the cracks of a system that wasn't designed for them.</p>
                <p>In the Inland Empire and communities like it across California, the shortage of primary care providers and mental health specialists means that <strong>getting help often feels impossible</strong> — even for those who are actively seeking it.</p>
                <p>Navigating insurance, finding in-network providers, understanding medications, and accessing support all require time, resources, and knowledge that many people simply don't have. MindConnect was built to bridge every one of those gaps.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-stack reveal">
                <div class="big-stat-card">
                    <div class="big-stat-num">60M</div>
                    <div class="big-stat-text">
                        <h4>Americans Affected</h4>
                        <p>Living with mental illness each year, per the National Institute of Health</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="big-stat-card">
                    <div class="big-stat-num">500K+</div>
                    <div class="big-stat-text">
                        <h4>People in Our Region</h4>
                        <p>Affected in our immediate area — millions more nationwide remain underserved</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="big-stat-card">
                    <div class="big-stat-num">35</div>
                    <div class="big-stat-text">
                        <h4>PCPs per 100K Residents</h4>
                        <p>Far below the national recommendation, leaving a critical care gap</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
 
<!-- SOLUTION / PILLARS -->
<section class="solution-section">
    <div class="solution-inner">
        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section-tag">Our Approach</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">How We're Closing the Gap</h2>
            <p class="section-sub">MindConnect's model is built on three core pillars that work together to create a complete support system for every individual.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillars-grid reveal">
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
                <h3>Connect to Resources</h3>
                <p>We map the landscape of available care in your area and connect you directly to the providers, programs, and support systems that fit your needs — cutting through the confusion.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
                <h3>Provide Peer Support</h3>
                <p>Certified peer support specialists — many with lived experience — walk alongside you, offering authentic guidance, accountability, and someone who truly understands.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
                <h3>Ensure No One Is Alone</h3>
                <p>From 24/7 access to crisis support to ongoing check-ins and community programs, we ensure that every person in our network has consistent human connection and support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
 
<!-- VISION -->
<section class="vision-section">
    <div class="vision-inner">
        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section-tag">Our Vision</div>
            <h2>A Future Where Care is Accessible for Everyone</h2>
            <p>We're building a future where your zip code, income level, or insurance status doesn't determine whether you can access quality mental health support.</p>
            <p>Available in English and Spanish, designed for underserved communities, and built on genuine human connection — MindConnect meets you where you are.</p>
        </div>
 
        <div class="values-grid reveal">
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-card-icon">🌎</div>
                <div>
                    <h4>Language Access</h4>
                    <p>All services available in English and Spanish, with plans to expand to additional languages as we grow.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-card-icon">💰</div>
                <div>
                    <h4>No Cost Barriers</h4>
                    <p>We work with all income levels and connect patients to financial assistance, free clinics, and sliding-scale care.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-card-icon">🤝</div>
                <div>
                    <h4>Community-Rooted</h4>
                    <p>Founded in the Inland Empire, we understand the unique challenges of our communities from the inside.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-card-icon">🔬</div>
                <div>
                    <h4>Evidence-Based</h4>
                    <p>Every program is developed with and reviewed by certified mental health professionals and clinical researchers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
 
        <div class="reveal">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Join Our Mission →</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
 
<footer>
    <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-logo">MindConnect</div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="services.html">Services</a>
            <a href="network.html">Network</a>
            <a href="mission.html">Mission</a>
            <a href="about.html">About</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;">© 2025 MindConnect.</div>
    </div>
</footer>
 
<script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('in-view'); });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });
    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
 
